nodes.text: The Dewback Ramblers were a band led by Blerx Tango during the Galactic Civil War.

After the Battle of Yavin, the band was based out of the Lucky Star cantina in Mos Entha. The band was led by the kloo horn player Blerx Tango, and staffed by three other members. The members consisted of a slitherhorn player named Jakko Mixon, an ommni box player named Mellaw Doowon, and a mandoviol player named Baze Joz.
Circa 1 ABY, three of the members got in trouble, including with the Galactic Empire, and had to be rescued by a spacer employed by Blerx.

The Dewback Ramblers appeared in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
